<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.2.14">
<l>entoṇṭai vāycciṅka vāveṉ ṟeṭuttukkoṇ</l>
<l>ṭantoṇṭai vāyamu tātarit tāycciyar</l>
<l>tantoṇṭai vāyāl tarukkip parukumic</l>
<l>centoṇṭai vāyvantu kāṇīrē cēyiḻai yīrvantu kāṇīrē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Red-jewelled Ladies, come and see this red toṇṭai [fruit] mouth</l>
<l>that was zealously drunk in by the toṇṭai [fruit] mouths of cowherdesses</l>
<l>craving the nectar of [his] beautiful toṇṭai [fruit] mouth taking [him] up saying,</l>
<l>“come our lion with the toṇṭai [fruit] mouth.” Come and see!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
